        <h1>Vision</h1>The student of the Faculty of Engineering of the University of San Carlos de Guatemala will be recognized as a senior professional, based on the knowledge incorporated in the curriculum of studies to train students holistically giving them the appropriate tools for his professional development

        <h1>Mission</h1>Develop in the student the competences that guarantee the successful in building the knowledge through the different learning styles and foster permanent research to enable a better quality of life to the community. Taking into account the options of the current market in the country (logistics, administration, information technology, finance, accounting, commercial, etc.), and also the international market, do to nowadays high global demand and competitiveness.

